wikimedia-license-links:
Links to the licenses used by most Wikimedia projects. Warning: the correct default licenses links are to the creativecommons.org ([https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-sa/4.0/] or e.g. [https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-sa/4.0/deed.fr]) and fsf.org ([https://www.gnu.org/copyleft/fdl.html]) pages, which should be used in the translations to languages other than English. Customisation may be possible on local wikis upon community consensus.

This message is used as a parameter for:
* {{msg-mw|wikimedia-discussiontools-replywidget-terms-click}}
