wikimedia-globalblocking-ipblocked-xff:
A message shown to users who have one or more proxies in their XFF header whose IP are blocked.

Parameters:
* $1 - username
* $2 - wikiname
* $3 - reason
* $4 - start timestamp of block; localized timestamp
* $5 - expiry timestamp of block; localized timestamp or the message {{msg-mw|Infiniteblock}}
* $6 - IP address which is blocked

Refers to:
* {{msg-mw|wikimedia-globalblocking-blockedtext-on-proxy}}
* {{msg-mw|globalblocking-blockedtext-proxy|$7}}
* {{msg-mw|blockedtext-include-details-queries}}
* {{msg-mw|wikimedia-globalblocking-blockedtext-mistake}}

It is a customised version of {{msg-mw|globalblocking-ipblocked-xff}}.

